{"tid":253650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥：D 女 仔 鍾 意 我 有 才 華","createTime":"2017-05-22T14:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T09:46:12.000Z","uid":35964,"like":5,"dislike":225,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3de22df4e4986f6fc4ba4008fc42bdbe4b225688","tid":253650,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"吳業坤最近被指髮線後移，他直言現在整頭髮時都很費時，又自嘲說：「依家駁髮，等啲頭髮睇起嚟厚一啲。」吳業坤又透露，有一些生髮公司找他幫忙貼文宣傳，但自己想找一個長遠的合作，「開始感覺到要用一世嘅時間，去處理頭髮數量愈嚟愈少嘅問題，而且已經擔心，髮線後移會遺傳到下一代。」問他會否害怕嚇跑女生，他自信地笑指：「唔怕，啲女仔鍾意我有才華，唔理我嘅五官。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/5/1495398776_e0-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F5%2F1495398776_e0-1280w.jpg&h=12143684&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb9e177077e83032f02fbc0c154ec765b8b5f9f1","tid":253650,"uid":140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3a5cea51e9d5a5f3994a4e807b35d90f20b2bd","tid":253650,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"我兩樣都鍾意"},{"pid":"49631594a956d42d78632c05ee0544f6ac3d994a","tid":253650,"uid":828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"幾時開棟篤笑"},{"pid":"c12d3bb79734757d6d14aecf4a3112c835a6f704","tid":253650,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"放心你都唔會有下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2338092b71a4eb8ded1d100446c2d18c6c118ce0","tid":253650,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"原來佢仲未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排冇乜聽到關於佢嘅嘢 仲以為佢死左"},{"pid":"f6fbcc29ea2a5015e1ee8433a44381cf54bf635b","tid":253650,"uid":49128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy